I caught onto their game.

00:15:34.976 --> 00:15:38.188 position:50% align:center
That said, I did keep a
backup for my own records.

00:15:39.272 --> 00:15:40.482 position:50% align:center
Nice going.

00:15:40.565 --> 00:15:43.276 position:50% align:center
This way, we can pinpoint
the areas we need.

00:15:49.532 --> 00:15:51.284 position:50% align:center
At those coordinates,

00:15:51.368 --> 00:15:54.704 position:50% align:center
I'm detecting some abnormal
readings, which means.

00:15:54.788 --> 00:15:56.790 position:50% align:center
We're about to find just
what we're looking for,

00:15:56.873 --> 00:15:59.376 position:50% align:center
so I say we run the program now!

00:15:59.459 --> 00:16:02.128 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:16:05.173 --> 00:16:08.051 position:50% align:center
Tell me, who are you?

00:16:12.305 --> 00:16:14.474 position:50% align:center
It's... me!

00:16:18.561 --> 00:16:22.816 position:50% align:center
But how? Why?
I don't understand.

00:16:22.899 --> 00:16:24.359 position:50% align:center
I'm lost.

00:16:28.446 --> 00:16:31.908 position:50% align:center
[YUITO sighs]

00:16:31.991 --> 00:16:35.453 position:50% align:center
So, who... am I?

00:16:37.288 --> 00:16:39.457 position:50% align:center
[LUKA]
Use the SAS cables!

00:16:41.960 --> 00:16:43.670 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Huh?

00:16:46.506 --> 00:16:47.841 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:16:49.426 --> 00:16:52.554 position:50% align:center
What's this? Huh?

00:16:52.637 --> 00:16:53.388 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
What?

00:16:53.471 --> 00:16:58.476 position:50% align:center
[YUITO screams]

00:17:00.812 --> 00:17:02.022 position:50% align:center
[SHIDEN]
Hm?

00:17:08.278 --> 00:17:09.821 position:50% align:center
I knocked him out for now.

00:17:09.904 --> 00:17:11.573 position:50% align:center
Good thinking.

00:17:11.656 --> 00:17:13.283 position:50% align:center
We should get started.

00:17:20.832 --> 00:17:23.793 position:50% align:center
[ARASHI] Remember everything
you can about Yuito!

00:17:23.877 --> 00:17:25.795 position:50% align:center
[HANABI, LUKA]
Yuito!

00:17:28.048 --> 00:17:32.052 position:50% align:center
[YUITO grunts]

00:17:32.135 --> 00:17:35.055 position:50% align:center
[ARASHI]
Okay here goes.

00:17:35.138 --> 00:17:37.766 position:50% align:center
[SHIDEN] We just have
to concentrate on Yuito.

00:17:39.142 --> 00:17:43.021 position:50% align:center
[KAGERO]
Everything depends on this.

00:17:43.104 --> 00:17:45.940 position:50% align:center
[KYOKA] All of us are
here by your side, Yuito.

00:18:03.541 --> 00:18:05.251 position:50% align:center
[LUKA]
Yuito.

00:18:05.335 --> 00:18:07.504 position:50% align:center
[GEMMA]
Yuito.

00:18:07.587 --> 00:18:09.339 position:50% align:center
[TSUGUMI]
Yuito.

00:18:09.422 --> 00:18:11.466 position:50% align:center
[HANABI]
Yuito.

00:18:11.549 --> 00:18:12.467 position:50% align:center
[KYOKA]
Yuito.

00:18:12.550 --> 00:18:19.391 position:50% align:center
[ALL]
Yuito... Yuito... Yuito...

00:18:40.245 --> 00:18:43.998 position:50% align:center
[KASANE] Yuito. I don't
have time to explain.

00:18:44.082 --> 00:18:46.292 position:50% align:center
You must go on living.

00:18:46.376 --> 00:18:50.005 position:50% align:center
So please, take this!

00:18:50.088 --> 00:18:54.342 position:50% align:center
[grunts]
Kasane?

00:18:57.595 --> 00:19:01.182 position:50% align:center
Hold on. Where am I?

00:19:04.602 --> 00:19:07.230 position:50% align:center
I'm lost. What's happening?

00:19:17.615 --> 00:19:19.784 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Dad?

00:19:19.868 --> 00:19:23.621 position:50% align:center
[ALL]
Yuito... Yuito... Yuito...

00:19:23.705 --> 00:19:26.916 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
They're calling out to me.

00:19:27.000 --> 00:19:34.007 position:50% align:center
[ALL]
Yuito... Yuito... Yuito...

00:19:45.268 --> 00:19:48.605 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Right, I have to get back!

00:19:48.688 --> 00:19:50.106 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:19:54.194 --> 00:19:55.737 position:50% align:center
[gasps]

00:20:00.784 --> 00:20:02.369 position:50% align:center
Mom, it's you!

00:20:04.704 --> 00:20:06.164 position:50% align:center
Yuito.

00:20:09.459 --> 00:20:13.213 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
I remembered, I'm so glad.

00:20:15.715 --> 00:20:22.347 position:50% align:center
[HANABI whimpers]
Yuito! Open your eyes, already!

00:20:22.430 --> 00:20:24.182 position:50% align:center
Yuito!

00:20:29.854 --> 00:20:31.648 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:20:31.731 --> 00:20:35.777 position:50% align:center
[YUITO] Huh? That's weird.
Was I dreaming all this time?

00:20:35.860 --> 00:20:36.861 position:50% align:center
Hanabi!

00:20:36.945 --> 00:20:39.280 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]

00:20:39.364 --> 00:20:41.199 position:50% align:center
Yuito! You're okay?

00:20:41.282 --> 00:20:44.744 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Oh, wow. You're all here.

00:20:44.828 --> 00:20:45.745 position:50% align:center
I don't get it.

00:20:45.829 --> 00:20:47.163 position:50% align:center
[HANABI gasps]
Yuito!

00:20:47.247 --> 00:20:48.665 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:20:48.748 --> 00:20:51.001 position:50% align:center
[CITIZENS chattering]

00:20:51.084 --> 00:20:53.378 position:50% align:center
[MALE ANNOUNCER A] Please listen
for an important message.

00:20:53.461 --> 00:20:56.548 position:50% align:center
We have imposed an official
curfew for this evening.

00:20:56.631 --> 00:21:00.051 position:50% align:center
Please stay at home or indoors
until further instructed.

00:21:00.135 --> 00:21:03.221 position:50% align:center
We also ask that you ignore the
misinformation that is currently

00:21:03.304 --> 00:21:04.389 position:50% align:center
being spread...

00:21:04.472 --> 00:21:05.807 position:50% align:center
[MAN B] What's he
mean "misinformation"?

00:21:05.890 --> 00:21:08.184 position:50% align:center
[WOMAN B] Ugh, I swear,
it's always something!

00:21:08.268 --> 00:21:09.728 position:50% align:center
[MAN C]
We're not allowed to be outside?

00:21:09.811 --> 00:21:11.521 position:50% align:center
[WOMAN C]
The moon's about to attack!

00:21:11.604 --> 00:21:13.857 position:50% align:center
[MAN D] The media works
for the government.

00:21:13.940 --> 00:21:17.360 position:50% align:center
[MAN E] What are they gonna do,
go against the government?

00:21:18.528 --> 00:21:20.280 position:50% align:center
Now that it's gotten this ugly,

00:21:20.363 --> 00:21:23.908 position:50% align:center
the politicians won't be able
to control the narrative.

00:21:23.992 --> 00:21:25.452 position:50% align:center
[KYOKA]
He's right.

00:21:25.535 --> 00:21:27.620 position:50% align:center
Even the strongest censorship
in the world won't be enough

00:21:27.704 --> 00:21:29.664 position:50% align:center
to muzzle public opinion.

00:21:32.167 --> 00:21:35.462 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Wait, Naomi? I'm sorry.

00:21:35.545 --> 00:21:37.380 position:50% align:center
[YUITO] If Kaito hadn't
hidden everything,

00:21:37.464 --> 00:21:38.923 position:50% align:center
maybe things would be different.

00:21:39.007 --> 00:21:42.844 position:50% align:center
[KASANE] We've lost so much,
it's time to make things right.

00:21:42.927 --> 00:21:45.305 position:50% align:center
We're going to
change New Himuka,

00:21:45.388 --> 00:21:48.433 position:50% align:center
so that our sacrifices
won't be in vain.

00:21:48.516 --> 00:21:51.644 position:50% align:center
[TSUGUMI]
Hm? Someone's here, look.

00:21:56.274 --> 00:21:57.484 position:50% align:center
[YUITO gasps]

00:21:59.486 --> 00:22:01.029 position:50% align:center
[YUITO]
Major General!

00:22:03.490 --> 00:22:07.118 position:50% align:center
Thank goodness.
I found you again.

00:22:07.202 --> 00:22:09.662 position:50% align:center
I've been searching
this whole time.

00:22:09.746 --> 00:22:11.331 position:50% align:center
Are you all right?

00:22:11.414 --> 00:22:14.084 position:50% align:center
[FUBUKI]
Pay no mind...

00:22:14.167 --> 00:22:16.670 position:50% align:center
All that matters is
that we're together now.

00:22:16.753 --> 00:22:18.755 position:50% align:center
We have to find somewhere safe.

00:22:18.838 --> 00:22:20.882 position:50% align:center
I must tell you--

00:22:20.965 --> 00:22:24.636 position:50% align:center
[gasps]
Oh, no! Major General Fubuki!

